Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.78,0:00:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛逝的秒針 劃過天際的彗星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.53,0:00:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現今社會人心疲憊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.49,0:00:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南的推理是一帖良藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.68,0:00:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天偵探團碰上大麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.50,0:00:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藉由智慧與勇氣的團隊合作度過難關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.47,0:00:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.17,0:00:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.14,0:00:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.22,0:00:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.87,0:01:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年偵探團遇難事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.73,0:02:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 元太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.36,0:02:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.48,0:02:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…你們沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.39,0:02:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才在看旁邊沒有注意到你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.44,0:02:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.21,0:02:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個暑假好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.64,0:02:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這一次到海邊來度假真是太值得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.84,0:02:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日 就是那個春日財團的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.44,0:02:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 我就是小開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.39,0:02:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我現在還是個在我爸羽翼下度日的大少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.51,0:03:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我們這樣不是給你添麻煩了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.20,0:03:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都坐上來真不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.16,0:03:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人多一點才有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.52,0:03:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不對 小忍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.02,0:03:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你們還真叫人羡慕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.81,0:03:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跟自己喜歡的人到這裡潛水真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.93,0:03:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的人啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.24,0:03:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我沒有大少爺這個身份的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.22,0:03:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小忍還會不會這麼喜歡我就不知道囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.01,0:03:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輝彥 我才不會這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.75,0:03:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳就說實話吧 小忍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.28,0:03:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人搞什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.91,0:03:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然跟女朋友吵架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.25,0:03:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.59,0:03:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來叔叔到底到哪里釣魚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.43,0:03:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說他到這一帶最大的一個池穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.43,0:03:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在天亮之前就出門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.74,0:03:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過好像不是到海邊去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.64,0:03:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得他說是個池塘的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.56,0:03:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是海邊的池塘嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.24,0:04:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了 又來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.42,0:04:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是大豐收
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.17,0:04:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.78,0:04:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小忍小姐已經回去了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.99,0:04:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道在鬧什麼彆扭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.69,0:04:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她常這個樣子 不用放在心上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.15,0:04:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她鬧脾氣的人明明是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.75,0:04:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人從剛剛就很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.49,0:04:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大豐收…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.13,0:04:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.74,0:04:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你挺厲害的嘛 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.36,0:04:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個池穴在哪裡啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.07,0:04:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想要釣釣看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.55,0:04:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…這可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.98,0:04:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.47,0:04:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那是一個釣友偷偷告訴我的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.58,0:04:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是我們之間的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.44,0:04:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.84,0:04:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來玩沙灘排球吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.65,0:04:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.97,0:04:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去那邊玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.99,0:04:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你也一起來玩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.13,0:05:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個好像是石雕吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.93,0:05:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.68,0:05:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.46,0:05:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然不是到海邊怎麼會掉到海魚呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.29,0:05:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看八成是在釣魚場釣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.16,0:05:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我毛利小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.47,0:05:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這滿肚子的才華可不只是做偵探而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.34,0:05:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利小五郎…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.13,0:05:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哪位啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.88,0:05:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又把球打到界外了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.18,0:05:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.89,0:05:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面還有一張紙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.21,0:05:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道這上面到底寫些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.33,0:05:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是藏寶圖啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.59,0:05:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這好像電影跟小說的情節哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.65,0:06:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.12,0:06:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這個是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.99,0:06:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SOS 小忍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.09,0:06:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.74,0:06:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小忍姐姐她怎麼會求救呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.72,0:06:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道她被海水沖走了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.48,0:06:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為她已經回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.21,0:06:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來這個女人還在這兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.80,0:06:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.25,0:06:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她常這個樣子 每次都搞這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.61,0:06:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為的就是讓我擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.64,0:06:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個女人還真是傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.85,0:06:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.54,0:06:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要滿潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.39,0:06:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就再去釣一次好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.09,0:06:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家海邊太危險了 不能到海邊去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.46,0:06:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 如果真的是小忍姐姐在求救的話就糟糕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.61,0:06:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣我們就去調查看看好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.83,0:06:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是去哪裡調查呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.76,0:06:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她在無人島上的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.80,0:06:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就太遠了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.42,0:06:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 這就時間上來說是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.50,0:06:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張紙還沒被太陽曬乾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.28,0:07:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小忍姐姐一定在離這裡不遠的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.15,0:07:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.93,0:07:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你絕對不要讓春日哥哥離開妳的視線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.21,0:07:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.38,0:07:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事拜託妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.56,0:07:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等 你們要去哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.34,0:07:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我就再去挑戰一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.95,0:07:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也跟你一起去吧 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.87,0:07:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.29,0:07:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個池塘對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.13,0:07:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附近這一帶我可是玩得不能再熟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.39,0:07:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.82,0:07:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 我們差不多該回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.16,0:07:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們大家都這麼任性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.13,0:07:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近到這裡來的年輕人真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.97,0:07:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爺爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.59,0:07:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.58,0:07:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.40,0:07:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們做什麼海水浴 又搞什麼潛水的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.29,0:07:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我們的海都給弄髒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.87,0:07:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.88,0:07:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.10,0:07:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.03,0:08:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問你知不知道那個瓶子是從哪裡漂過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.23,0:08:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.53,0:08:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.71,0:08:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.32,0:08:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你帶那個幹什麼 我們可不是要趁退潮到海邊玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.04,0:08:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要你管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.91,0:08:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易到海邊來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.27,0:08:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能沒抓到扇貝、蛤蜊跟鰻魚就這麼空手回去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.90,0:08:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太你這個人就只知道吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.18,0:08:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到我們就來吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.84,0:08:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看你們想到的都只是玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.10,0:08:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒有事吧 步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.38,0:08:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.84,0:08:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要滿潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.25,0:08:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳要小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.62,0:08:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.24,0:08:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小忍姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.42,0:08:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是她 沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.32,0:08:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快 海水已經開始流進洞窟裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.37,0:09:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小忍姐姐 妳不要緊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.30,0:09:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳醒一醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.40,0:09:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小忍姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.23,0:09:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.48,0:09:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你們啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.18,0:09:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.63,0:09:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼事 小忍姐姐？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.74,0:09:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人說要帶我去一起玩他最得意的潛水運動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.62,0:09:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說滿潮的時候有個洞窟就會消失在大海裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.19,0:09:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.14,0:09:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我喝了他帶來的飲料以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.82,0:09:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就突然好想睡覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.54,0:10:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那瓶飲料裡面加了安眠藥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.53,0:10:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想讓別人以為這是件意外將妳殺害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.84,0:10:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小忍姐姐在這裡溺死的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.11,0:10:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就有不在場的證明了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.70,0:10:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他差點撞到我們和我們相識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.95,0:10:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有故意跟妳吵架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.12,0:10:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是他算計好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.06,0:10:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是為什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.88,0:10:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就是警察的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.99,0:10:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們快點離開這裡去報警吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.63,0:10:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你看那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.28,0:10:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潮水已經漲到這裡來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.27,0:10:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.56,0:10:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們快點回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.98,0:10:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快點離開船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.83,0:10:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船已經被撞破了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.34,0:10:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.21,0:10:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.32,0:10:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦才好呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.55,0:10:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在海浪這麼大 根本不可能游泳出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.86,0:11:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我們身邊還有一個意識不太清楚的小忍小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.82,0:11:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.15,0:11:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰來救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.52,0:11:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還不想死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.00,0:11:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家冷靜一點 先不要慌張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.53,0:11:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說起來是很容易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.25,0:11:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是海水把這裡都填滿的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.54,0:11:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家就要淹死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.41,0:11:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.79,0:11:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.09,0:11:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.96,0:11:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.54,0:11:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是螢火蟲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.44,0:11:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢火蟲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.19,0:11:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.92,0:11:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確不太對勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.69,0:11:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個一天裡面會有兩次被海水填滿的洞窟怎麼會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.29,0:11:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.39,0:11:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.45,0:11:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個洞窟有別的出口 螢火蟲是從那邊進來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.85,0:11:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.66,0:11:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有別的出入口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.37,0:11:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今我們也只有從那裡脫逃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.88,0:11:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那個出入口如果人不能通過的話呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.71,0:11:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.27,0:11:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.11,0:12:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們幾個可不是螢火蟲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.79,0:12:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔釣到的石雕比淡水魚大得多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.06,0:12:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身上卻還完全沒有傷痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.86,0:12:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可見那個出入口絕對沒有那麼小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.34,0:12:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些魚就是在黎明之前滿潮的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.18,0:12:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從大海的方向游進洞窟裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.48,0:12:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到水流到裡面以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.89,0:12:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔就從另一個入口釣到那些石雕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.12,0:12:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那裡一定是個大池塘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.48,0:12:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不是在海邊 還是能釣到海魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.79,0:12:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以大家才會把那裡叫做池穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.35,0:12:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.49,0:12:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.24,0:12:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了 叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.56,0:12:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為你是在釣魚場釣的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.04,0:12:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果待在這裡一定會淹死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.60,0:12:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信柯南不會說錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.36,0:12:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我們走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.06,0:12:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.68,0:12:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有水從上面掉下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.68,0:12:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.90,0:12:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不要嚇人好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.45,0:13:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.96,0:13:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們好像迷路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.83,0:13:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要走到哪裡才能夠出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.08,0:13:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果貿然前進只會迷路而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.05,0:13:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是再不快點的話 我們會被滿潮淹死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.54,0:13:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧 就隨便挑一條好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.97,0:13:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 元太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.00,0:13:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 怎麼是一條死路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.23,0:13:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是早就說過了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.63,0:13:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就跟螢火蟲出去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.49,0:13:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.43,0:13:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有螢火蟲的地方就可以通到出入口了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.78,0:13:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家現在就分頭找螢火蟲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.76,0:13:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.88,0:13:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也來幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.39,0:13:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經沒問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.24,0:13:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡沒有發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.25,0:13:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.14,0:13:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.50,0:13:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.94,0:13:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.29,0:13:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.26,0:13:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.67,0:14:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右邊還是左邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.98,0:14:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在只能二選一了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.50,0:14:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我們再來找螢火蟲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.60,0:14:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用 哪裡都找不到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.93,0:14:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就要在這裡等死了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.83,0:14:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要說這種不吉利的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.70,0:14:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在該怎麼辦 柯南？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.59,0:14:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有別的辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.88,0:14:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.05,0:14:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.18,0:14:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是利用石頭的回聲來做判斷的對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.18,0:14:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果回聲大的話就表示前面是條死路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.79,0:14:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變小的話就表示前面還有路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.69,0:14:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.52,0:14:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.51,0:15:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 用力拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.21,0:15:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也出點力嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.12,0:15:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.30,0:15:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼聲音？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.24,0:15:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小鳥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.27,0:15:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.97,0:15:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想牠們也許是為了找尋食物才進來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.97,0:15:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些鳥都朝著出入口的方向飛出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.82,0:15:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我們去追牠們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.31,0:15:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.81,0:15:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.21,0:15:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍著點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.02,0:15:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 我們用跑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.38,0:15:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.55,0:15:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.52,0:15:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這根本不痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.69,0:16:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在又聽不到聲音了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.10,0:16:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.20,0:16:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經飛出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.75,0:16:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們太慢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.00,0:16:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鳥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.33,0:16:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我嚇了一大跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.67,0:16:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.29,0:16:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想馬上就要到滿潮的高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.59,0:16:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 他們到底跑哪去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.17,0:16:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.14,0:16:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你絕對不要讓春日哥哥離開妳的視線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.83,0:16:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.82,0:16:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要回去的話可得把東西一起帶走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.74,0:16:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爺爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.04,0:16:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳知道這附近能釣到最多魚的地方在哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.07,0:16:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在往哪邊 柯南？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.01,0:16:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪邊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.02,0:16:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.61,0:16:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.41,0:16:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.41,0:16:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.20,0:17:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.55,0:17:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快抓住我 小忍姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.11,0:17:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.08,0:17:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.17,0:17:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.47,0:17:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道我們會被沖進死路裡面去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.95,0:17:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手電筒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.23,0:17:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好黑哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.72,0:17:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.01,0:17:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.34,0:17:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們幾個一定是不知不覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.95,0:17:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走到了洞窟的正上方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.41,0:17:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在海水應該很快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.03,0:17:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要從另外一個出口流出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.19,0:17:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是在哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.13,0:17:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子根本就不知道哪裡是上下左右了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.89,0:18:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底會到哪裡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.96,0:18:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.61,0:18:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了 來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.27,0:18:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.60,0:18:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被卡住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.22,0:18:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 洞窟太窄元太過不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.62,0:18:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救生衣堵住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.97,0:18:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要脫掉就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.69,0:18:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 只好把它弄破了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.97,0:18:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 弄不破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.81,0:18:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有什麼方法…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.34,0:18:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.22,0:18:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙鏟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.52,0:18:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.83,0:18:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.50,0:18:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我快撐不住了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.86,0:19:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為死定了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.08,0:19:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於得救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.40,0:19:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.73,0:19:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會到這裡來呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.16,0:19:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒錯 跟我想的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.00,0:19:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿潮的時候海水會流過洞窟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.49,0:19:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一口氣排到洞窟外的池穴來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.80,0:19:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是池穴的水面沒有上升
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.69,0:19:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為海水不單只從洞窟流出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.04,0:19:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還同時從岩穴下面的通道不斷地將海水排出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.37,0:19:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這個通道因為太小了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.55,0:19:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以滿潮的時候流出去的水就相對比較少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.80,0:19:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個到底是從哪裡到這兒來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.11,0:19:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就想可能會發生這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.06,0:19:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真被我料中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.34,0:19:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我跟你來是對的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.93,0:19:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.32,0:19:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.14,0:19:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.06,0:19:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.54,0:19:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輝彥 快住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.96,0:20:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想要幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.42,0:20:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.58,0:20:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 你要是真地開槍的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.51,0:20:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你故意讓一切看起來像是意外的苦心就白費了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.13,0:20:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為我不敢開槍是不是 小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.91,0:20:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要對付你們有足夠的子彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.81,0:20:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.16,0:20:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.45,0:20:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點住手 輝彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.38,0:20:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真正想殺的人應該是我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.49,0:20:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這跟那個孩子一點關係也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.05,0:20:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這事情就要怪妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.71,0:20:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳從世界上消失就沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.97,0:20:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.38,0:20:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼要這樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.29,0:20:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經照我爸爸的意思跟一個富家千金訂婚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.29,0:20:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想離開家 跟妳貧苦一輩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.22,0:20:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我寧願一輩子做我的大少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.19,0:20:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太過分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.46,0:20:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個傢伙太過分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.41,0:20:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我唯一的王牌 馬力特強的球鞋並沒有穿在腳上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.72,0:20:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有其它武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.14,0:20:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來這次真的要沒命了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.43,0:20:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然真相被你們知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.32,0:20:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就沒有再利用你們的必要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.07,0:21:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就讓你們幾個全部到海裡去餵魚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.07,0:21:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這幾個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.27,0:21:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是禁止外人進入的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.64,0:21:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拋棄女人的男人 不可原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.86,0:21:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年偵探團 大勝利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.51,0:23:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從推理或懸疑的角度來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.40,0:23:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要解決這一次的事件的確不容易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.71,0:23:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過對某個人來說就更慘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.75,0:23:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直亂來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.92,0:23:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個要沒收
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.23,0:23:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.36,0:23:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到現在你還聽不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.27,0:23:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後 叔叔整整被那個老先生教訓了一個鐘頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.30,0:23:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為滿潮的時候水面會上升很危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.10,0:23:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會禁止人進去釣魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.21,0:23:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會被人家罵也是很自然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.53,0:23:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神陣內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.02,0:23:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快束手就擒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.83,0:23:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.57,0:23:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手現在還在七樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.20,0:23:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才看到他的影子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.52,0:24:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼死神陣內要開槍呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.03,0:24:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 他到底怎麼避開警方的視線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.32,0:24:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又躲到這棟大樓的哪裡去了呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.84,0:24:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.13,0:24:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神陣內殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.98,0:24:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.51,0:24:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電梯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.58,0:24:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回是謎樣的殺手登場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.01,0:24:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是謎樣殺手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.97,0:24:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.17,0:24:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我才是
